reviewText: If you haven't seen this series it's a must. It's great and funny.
Perfect condition. Good price. These are hard to find so I grab them whenever I can. Now I am only missing season #5 so I actually haven't watched this one yet.
The series is fun and tasteful. It allows Muslims to have fun with their own religion and teach others that we aren't that different after all.
Wonderful wrap up for the series, funny and touching. Discs arrived early and in great condition.  Watched them all one rainy Saturday. Perfect!
